<br>
I have stopped running formal raids.  I've been hoping someone who is reliable and has the right support will be willing to step forward to run these.<br>
<br>
In the interm I'll be running the occasional plane raid as my time and the rotations allow.  This means something like perhaps 1 a month or every 6 weeks.  It will all depend on my Real Life commitments, Guild commitments, and Alliance commitments.  In the 2 months since I stopped doing these on a regular basis I have run 3 planar raids, so we do do them every couple of weeks.<br>
<br>
We just happen to be low on the rotation currently and with the Christmas season I dont want to stress anyone out.<br>
<br>
If anyone wants to try I'll be happy to schedule a plane raid day, which should probably be Fear since we've done Hate several times in a row already.  I'll be there to help run things and break whoever wants to do it in.  The idea is to eventually move someone else as the KCoG Plane Raid Liason in much the same way Azure has taken over from Kommisar from the Dragon Raids.<br>
<br>
In the meantime I do still function as the KCoG Plane Raid Liason and will run the occasional raid.  Next one probably wont be until Mid January, however, due to the numbers of people who are away for the holidays.<br>
<br>
Kellory Silverstar<br>
KCoG Plane Raid Liason<br>
